reviewText: A movie written as such by Sartre, and dealing with the form of bad faith known as second-guessing.  If only, if only...  JPS takes a subject that often arises--what if we had a second chance--and applies his materialism to it.  As frequently happens, divine intervention isn't all it's made out to be, ans Sartre's title echo's Pascal's wager:  "Vous tes embarqu."
